description:
Jazztrio BassDrumBone is celebrating their 40th anniversary at the ZomerJazzFietsTour 2017! Ray Anderson (trombone), Mark Helias (bass) and Gerry Hemingway (drums) have all paid their dues playing with various great names in jazz, but they always come back to share their love for musical communication, exciting sounds and... humor!

VPRO Vrije Geluiden is a music program made by the Dutch public broadcast organization VPRO.

http://vpro.nl/vrije-geluiden
https://www.zjft.nl
